			<h1
																									>NHS whistleblowers must be protected or there will be more deaths</h1>
		
					<p id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"																				>It is crucial that health service managers face up to mistakes and learn lessons from them</p>
		
		
  	</div>

